---
import DemoLayout from '../../../layouts/DemoLayout.astro';
---

<DemoLayout
  title="Cloudflare Images Solutions"
  description="Cloudflare offers two solutions: Images Transformations for on-the-fly optimization of externally-hosted images via URL or Workers, and Cloudflare Images as a managed service with integrated storage that automatically optimizes images for web delivery."
  category="Application Performance"
  labels={["Images", "Image Optimization", "Image Storage"]}
  lastUpdated="December 2025"
>

  <!-- Solution Overview -->
  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
    <h2 id="overview-heading">Solution Overview</h2>
    <p>Cloudflare offers two distinct approaches for <strong>image optimization</strong>:</p>

    <div class="solution-grid mt-1">
      <div class="solution-card solution-secondary">
        <h3>Cloudflare Images</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Managed hosting service</strong> with Cloudflare-managed backend storage. Upload images to
          Cloudflare and use it as your image hosting provider.
        </p>
        <p class="use-case">Best for: New projects, complete image management solution</p>
      </div>
      <div class="solution-card solution-primary">
        <h3>Image Transformations</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Optimization service</strong> for images hosted externally (Amazon S3, Cloudflare R2, or any
          origin server). Transform and resize on-demand.
        </p>
        <p class="use-case">Best for: Existing image infrastructure, external storage</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cloudflare Images Section -->
  <section aria-labelledby="cf-images-heading">
    <h2 id="cf-images-heading">Cloudflare Images</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Key Features</h3>

      <h4 class="subsection-heading">Storage &amp; Upload Options</h4>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Upload via custom path:</strong> Recommended for general use with API integration</li>
        <li><strong>Batch API upload:</strong> Efficient for large quantities of images</li>
        <li>
          <strong>
            <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/upload-images/direct-creator-upload/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
              Direct creator uploads
            </a>:
          </strong>
          {' '}One-time upload URLs for end-users and clients
        </li>
        <li><strong>Dashboard upload:</strong> Quick testing and manual uploads</li>
        <li><strong>Workers upload:</strong> Integration with Cloudflare Developer Platform</li>
      </ul>

      <h4 class="subsection-heading">Delivery Options</h4>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>
          <strong>
            <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/manage-images/create-variants/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
              Image Variants
            </a>:
          </strong>
          {' '}Create preset configurations for different use cases
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>
            <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/manage-images/enable-flexible-variants/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
              Flexible Variants
            </a>:
          </strong>
          {' '}Apply customizable transformation parameters on-demand
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>
            <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/manage-images/serve-images/serve-private-images/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
              Private Images
            </a>:
          </strong>
          {' '}Serve images using signed URL tokens for access control
        </li>
        <li><strong>Custom Domains:</strong> Serve images from your own domain</li>
      </ul>

      <h4 class="subsection-heading">URL Format</h4>
      <div class="url-format-block">
        <p><strong>Standard Domain:</strong></p>
        <code>https://imagedelivery.net/&lt;ACCOUNT_HASH&gt;/&lt;IMAGE_ID&gt;/&lt;VARIANT_NAME&gt;</code>
        <p class="mt-1"><strong>Custom Domain:</strong></p>
        <code>https://example.com/cdn-cgi/imagedelivery/&lt;ACCOUNT_HASH&gt;/&lt;IMAGE_ID&gt;/&lt;VARIANT_NAME&gt;</code>
      </div>

      <h4 class="subsection-heading">Dashboard Configuration</h4>
      <div class="img-container">
        <img
          src="/demos/performance/img/cf-account-images.png"
          alt="Cloudflare Images Dashboard Configuration"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Live Examples -->
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Live Examples</h3>

      <h4 class="subsection-heading">Original Image (Public Variant)</h4>
      <div class="img-container">
        <img
          src="https://imagedelivery.net/2sbFr08YIps0arOTfjTqvQ/315f4dee-cba5-4b44-b12c-b77cccc79a00/public"
          alt="Original demo image - public variant"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <code class="url-display">https://imagedelivery.net/2sbFr08YIps0arOTfjTqvQ/315f4dee-cba5-4b44-b12c-b77cccc79a00/public</code>
      <div class="btn-row mt-1">
        <a
          href="https://automatic-demo.com/cdn-cgi/imagedelivery/2sbFr08YIps0arOTfjTqvQ/315f4dee-cba5-4b44-b12c-b77cccc79a00/public"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer external"
          class="btn btn-primary"
        >
          View with Custom Domain
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="responsive-grid mt-2">
        <div>
          <h4 class="subsection-heading">Preset Variant Example</h4>
          <div class="img-container">
            <img
              src="https://imagedelivery.net/2sbFr08YIps0arOTfjTqvQ/315f4dee-cba5-4b44-b12c-b77cccc79a00/contain"
              alt="Preset variant example - contain fit"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <code class="url-display">.../contain</code>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="subsection-heading">Flexible Variant Example</h4>
          <div class="img-container">
            <img
              src="https://imagedelivery.net/2sbFr08YIps0arOTfjTqvQ/315f4dee-cba5-4b44-b12c-b77cccc79a00/w=250,quality=50,rotate=180"
              alt="Flexible variant example - width 250, quality 50, rotated 180 degrees"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <code class="url-display">.../w=250,quality=50,rotate=180</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image Transformations Section -->
  <section aria-labelledby="transforms-heading">
    <h2 id="transforms-heading">Image Transformations</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <p>
        Transform and optimize images stored on external origin servers (Amazon S3, Cloudflare R2, etc.) without
        migrating your storage.
      </p>

      <h3 class="subsection-heading">Three Transformation Methods</h3>

      <div class="method-card method-secondary">
        <h4>
          1.{' '}
          <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/transform-images/transform-via-url/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
            Transform via URL
          </a>
        </h4>
        <p>Simple URL-based transformations. Add parameters to your image URLs for on-the-fly optimization.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            Use <code class="inline-code">width=auto</code> for automatic sizing based on browser/device (Chromium only)
          </li>
          <li>
            Combine with <code class="inline-code">srcset</code> for{' '}
            <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/transform-images/make-responsive-images/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
              responsive images
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            Use <code class="inline-code">loading="lazy"</code> or{' '}
            <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/tutorials/optimize-mobile-viewing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
              eager loading
            </a>
            {' '}for mobile optimization
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-1"><strong>URL Format:</strong></p>
        <code>https://&lt;ZONE&gt;/cdn-cgi/image/&lt;OPTIONS&gt;/&lt;SOURCE-IMAGE&gt;</code>
      </div>

      <div class="method-card method-primary">
        <h4>
          2.{' '}
          <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/transform-images/transform-via-workers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
            Transform via Workers
          </a>
        </h4>
        <p>
          Maximum flexibility with programmatic control. Enables complex transformations including{' '}
          <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/transform-images/draw-overlays/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
            overlays and watermarks
          </a>.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Authentication and access control (Basic Auth, headers, cookies)</li>
          <li>Conditional logic (user-agent, HTTP method, request.cf properties)</li>
          <li>Multiple transformations in sequence</li>
          <li>API automation with tokens, SDKs, or Terraform</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="method-card method-secondary">
        <h4>
          3.{' '}
          <a href="https://blog.cloudflare.com/improve-your-media-pipelines-with-the-images-binding-for-cloudflare-workers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
            Transform via Images Binding
          </a>
        </h4>
        <p>
          Alternative to{' '}
          <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/transform-images/transform-via-workers/#fetch-options" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
            <em>fetch()</em>
          </a>
          {' '}for tighter integration with Cloudflare Developer Platform.
        </p>
        <p>Useful for multiple transformations and advanced workflows.</p>
      </div>

      <h4 class="subsection-heading">Code Examples</h4>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a href="https://gist.github.com/DavidJKTofan/31a3b6164dfdc6961c6910f7da9b9bf3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Resizing Example
        </a>
        <a href="https://gist.github.com/DavidJKTofan/405690937e86e517771f54c701ae48da" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Overlay Example
        </a>
        <a href="https://exif.automatic-demo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external" class="btn btn-primary">
          EXIF Protector Demo
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Interactive Demo -->
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Interactive Transformation Demo</h3>
      <p>
        <a href="/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Original Image
        </a>: 3 MB, 2419w &times; 3226h px, 72 DPI
      </p>

      <form id="transformForm" class="transform-form">
        <div class="form-grid">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="width">Width:</label>
            <input type="number" id="width" name="width" min="1" max="3000" value="800" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="height">Height:</label>
            <input type="number" id="height" name="height" min="1" max="3000" placeholder="Auto" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="quality">Quality (1-100):</label>
            <input type="number" id="quality" name="quality" min="1" max="100" value="75" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="blur">Blur (1-250):</label>
            <input type="number" id="blur" name="blur" min="1" max="250" placeholder="None" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="rotate">Rotate:</label>
            <select id="rotate" name="rotate">
              <option value="">None</option>
              <option value="90">90&deg;</option>
              <option value="180">180&deg;</option>
              <option value="270">270&deg;</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="fit">Fit:</label>
            <select id="fit" name="fit">
              <option value="scale-down">scale-down</option>
              <option value="contain">contain</option>
              <option value="cover">cover</option>
              <option value="crop">crop</option>
              <option value="pad">pad</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="form-hint">
          <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/transform-images/transform-via-url/#options" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
            View all available options
          </a>
        </p>
      </form>

      <div class="mt-1">
        <h4 class="subsection-heading">Transform URL:</h4>
        <code id="transformUrl" class="transform-url-display"></code>
        <div class="img-container mt-1">
          <img
            id="transformedImage"
            src="/cdn-cgi/image/width=800,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg"
            alt="Interactive transformation demo showing real-time parameter changes"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Advanced Examples -->
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Advanced Transformation Examples</h3>
      <div class="responsive-grid mt-1">
        <div>
          <h4 class="subsection-heading">Background Removal &amp; Zoom</h4>
          <div class="img-container">
            <img
              src="https://automatic-demo.com/cdn-cgi/image/gravity=auto,zoom=0.5,segment=foreground,background=white/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg"
              alt="Advanced transformation - foreground segmentation with background removal and zoom"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <code class="url-display">gravity=auto,zoom=0.5,segment=foreground,background=white</code>
          <div class="btn-row mt-1">
            <a
              href="https://automatic-demo.com/cdn-cgi/image/gravity=auto,zoom=0.5,segment=foreground,background=white/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer external"
              class="btn btn-secondary"
            >
              View Full Resolution
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="subsection-heading">How It Works</h4>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><strong>gravity=auto:</strong> Automatically detects and focuses on the main subject</li>
            <li><strong>zoom=0.5:</strong> Zooms into the subject at 50% magnification</li>
            <li><strong>segment=foreground:</strong> Separates the foreground subject from background</li>
            <li><strong>background=white:</strong> Replaces the background with white color</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="hint-text">
            Perfect for product photography, profile pictures, and content featuring people or objects.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Responsive Images -->
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Responsive Images Demo</h3>
      <p>
        Uses <code class="inline-code">srcset</code> to serve different sizes based on viewport:
      </p>
      <div class="img-container mt-1">
        <img
          srcset="/cdn-cgi/image/width=320,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg 320w,
                  /cdn-cgi/image/width=480,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg 480w,
                  /cdn-cgi/image/width=800,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg 800w,
                  /cdn-cgi/image/width=1200,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg 1200w"
          sizes="(max-width: 320px) 280px, (max-width: 480px) 440px, (max-width: 800px) 760px, 1000px"
          src="/cdn-cgi/image/width=800,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg"
          alt="Responsive image demo automatically adjusting to viewport size"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Lazy Loading -->
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Lazy Loading Demo</h3>
      <p>
        Images load only when entering viewport using <code class="inline-code">loading="lazy"</code>:
      </p>
      <div class="lazy-grid mt-1">
        <div class="img-container">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/cdn-cgi/image/width=800,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg" alt="Lazy loaded image example 1" />
        </div>
        <div class="img-container">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/cdn-cgi/image/width=800,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg" alt="Lazy loaded image example 2" />
        </div>
        <div class="img-container">
          <img loading="lazy" src="/cdn-cgi/image/width=800,quality=75/demos/performance/img/munich-original-img.jpeg" alt="Lazy loaded image example 3" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Considerations -->
  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="technical-heading">
    <h2 id="technical-heading">Technical Considerations</h2>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">Configuration Requirements</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li><strong>Custom Domains/Routes:</strong> Image Transformations require Workers Custom Domains or Routes</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Polish:</strong> Disable{' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/polish/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Polish</a>
        {' '}for Zones using Image Transformations, or use{' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/rules/configuration-rules/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Configuration Rules</a>
        {' '}for selective disabling
      </li>
      <li><strong>Zone Requirement:</strong> Transformations only apply to customer Zones, not Cloudflare domains (e.g., workers.dev)</li>
      <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> Set encryption mode to Full (minimum)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">Caching &amp; Performance</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>
        Images{' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/cache/concepts/default-cache-behavior/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">cache by default</a>
        {' '}or via Cache Rules/Cache-Control headers
      </li>
      <li>
        Review{' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/cache/how-to/purge-cache/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">purging options</a>
        {' '}when updates are needed
      </li>
      <li>
        Check{' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/transform-images/#supported-formats-and-limitations" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          supported formats and limitations
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">Alternative Storage Options</h3>
    <p>
      For other hosting options beyond Cloudflare Images, explore{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/platform/storage-options/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
        Cloudflare's storage solutions
      </a>
      {' '}including R2 Object Storage.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Resources -->
  <section class="card resources-card" aria-labelledby="resources-heading">
    <h2 id="resources-heading">Additional Resources</h2>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li><a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/images/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Cloudflare Images Documentation</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/examples/images-workers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Workers Example: Custom Domain with Images</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/reference-architecture/diagrams/storage/storing-user-generated-content/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Storing user generated content</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/reference-architecture/diagrams/content-delivery/optimizing-image-delivery-with-cloudflare-image-resizing-and-r2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Optimizing image delivery with Cloudflare image resizing and R2</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/reference-architecture/diagrams/serverless/serverless-image-content-management/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">Serverless image content management</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

</DemoLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Section spacing ===== */
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section > h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 3vw, 1.45rem);
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ===== Card ===== */
  .card {
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card h2, .card h3 {
    color: var(--secondary);
  }

  .card p, section > p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .resources-card {
    background-color: rgba(0, 81, 195, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  /* ===== Solution Grid ===== */
  .solution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .solution-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  .solution-card {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .solution-card h3 { margin-top: 0; color: var(--secondary); }

  .solution-secondary {
    background: rgba(0, 81, 195, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .solution-primary {
    background: rgba(246, 130, 31, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .use-case {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
  }

  /* ===== Method cards ===== */
  .method-card {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .method-card h4 { margin-top: 0; color: var(--secondary); }

  .method-secondary {
    background: rgba(0, 81, 195, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .method-primary {
    background: rgba(246, 130, 31, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
  }

  /* ===== Subsection headings ===== */
  .subsection-heading {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  /* ===== Feature list ===== */
  .feature-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== URL format block ===== */
  .url-format-block {
    background: var(--code-bg);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .url-format-block p { margin-bottom: 0.4rem !important; }

  .url-format-block code {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  /* ===== URL display code ===== */
  .url-display {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  /* ===== Image Container ===== */
  .img-container {
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .img-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ===== Responsive Grid ===== */
  .responsive-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .responsive-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  /* ===== Lazy Grid ===== */
  .lazy-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  /* ===== Transform form ===== */
  .transform-form {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--card);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .form-group label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group select {
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background-color: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--focus);
  }

  .form-hint {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  /* ===== Transform URL display ===== */
  .transform-url-display {
    display: block;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border-radius: 4px;
    word-break: break-all;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  /* ===== Inline code ===== */
  .inline-code {
    display: inline;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: #d63384;
  }

  /* ===== Hint text ===== */
  .hint-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  /* ===== Button Row ===== */
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
